short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Vitae.ai is a browser extension that helps you to prospect leads.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Vitae is a powerful contact prospecting and data enrichment tool, designed to streamline lead generation and sales processes. Similar to Apollo.io and Lusha, Vitae enables users to find key contact details and valuable business information, helping businesses connect with their ideal customers more efficiently. Perfect for sales teams, recruiters, and marketers, Vitae provides the data you need to enhance outreach and accelerate growth.
